{"body": "Unless I'm overlooking something this change will break all installations that have and use a local MTA.\r\n\r\nIn order to use most submission servers, one would need to specify a username and password. Changing the default port from 25 to 587 will still require everyone who currently overrides SMTP configuration to override it, to specify the username and password, but will break mail sending out of the box for those who have local MTAs.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1918801", "created_at": "2011-08-27T05:59:15Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2361#issuecomment-1918801", "updated_at": "2011-08-27T05:59:57Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 2361, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/p/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/p/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/p/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/p", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/p/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/p", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/p/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/1c7bded9fd1b6e5ca8e9f77a6222302c?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F67babe48f28145b5e7f3580a3fccd4e9.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/p/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/p/received_events", "gravatar_id": "1c7bded9fd1b6e5ca8e9f77a6222302c", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/p/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "p", "type": "User", "id": 125612, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/p/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523fcababd354364b901b0d1"}, "id": 1918801, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2361"}
